  dialogueLines:
  - ?????
  - Why have you come here, child?
  - "I\u2019m getting Taika back!"
  - "You\u2019ve charmed them, but I know they want to leave!"
  - Hahah! Really, now?
  - "I don\u2019t think so. Out there, they had nothing. But here?"
  - They can be the star of the show, every night, adored by the world.
  - "Do you really want to take that away from them? Tsk\u2026 What a good friend
    you are\u2026"
  - SHUT UP YOU CREEP!
  - ????
  - "You don\u2019t know what you\u2019re talking about!"
  - Taika is super talented, and they can start their own circus without you pulling
    from the strings like some crazy puppeteer!!!
  - ' Every member here could, and that is why you need them!'
  - Because you are a talentless, creepy loser whose show SUCKS!!!
  - " I\u2019m taking Taika with me, and if you try to stop us, I will KICK YOUR
    ASS! "
  - ........
  - Issssss that sssssso?
  - Come on then, kid.
  - Entertain me before I rip out your ssssssssoul!!!!
